} 13. h3 b5 14. g4 Na6 {It's already annoying to see ... Nb4 coming, and it's even worse to prevent it.} 15. a3 {This is only making things worse.} b4 {Black opens the queenside and can bring the knight to b4 anyway if White takes.} *

