d3 , we are forced to do something about this move. Pushing ... b4 is a natural option, but White could organize to bring the b1 -knight to c4 .} bxa4 {I like this approach. White will have to take it back, and in the meantime, we will react in the center.} 11. Nc3 Nbd7 12. Nxa4 c5 {Black will trade in the center; the position is roughly balanced and almost symmetrical.} *

