ght and chase our c6 -knight and d6 -bishop. But right now, there is no rush in taKing on d4 .} Re8 11. h3 {White has tried this waiting move a few times. White waits for Black to show their hands but also prevents ... Bg4 and can sometimes go g4 later.} exd4 12. exd4 Bf5 {Black takes control of the e4 -square and prevents Rb1 .} 13. c5 Bf8 14. Bf4 Nb4 {Black also takes control of the d5 -square now.} 15. Qb3 a5 16. Ne5 Be6 17. Qd1 Nbd5 {All this has been played in the game 0-1 Xiong-Tari, chess.com 2022, and I believe Black is already better thanks to the control of the center and lack of weaknesses.} *

